        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Linking Investors and Nursing Home Quality Act or the LINHQ Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes additional requirements for Medicare skilled nursing facilities and Medicaid nursing facilities with respect to ownership disclosures and quality control, including conditioning Medicare and Medicaid payment on timely ownership disclosures. The bill also establishes dedicated task forces to review disclosures, develop quality metrics, and report violations.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
